00:11:13,830 --> 00:11:17,230
but regular U.S. ship visits to Taiwan

275
00:11:17,230 --> 00:11:20,029
and to have ships in Taiwanese ports,

276
00:11:20,029 --> 00:11:21,940
to have troops in Taiwan,

