00:11:21,940 --> 00:11:26,779
perhaps a few thousand troops on a rotational
basis,

278
00:11:26,779 --> 00:11:30,110
to have military exercises with the Taiwanese
military,

279
00:11:30,110 --> 00:11:32,880
both at the training ranges in Taiwan

280
00:11:32,880 --> 00:11:35,790
and the United States to see regular exchanges

281
00:11:35,790 --> 00:11:39,790
of high level visitors from the United States
to Taiwan,

