00:12:01,940 --> 00:12:05,270
is very high over the next 10 years.

291
00:12:05,270 --> 00:12:08,720
So what was the concern people had

292
00:12:08,720 --> 00:12:11,000
about what China would do to the U.S.

293
00:12:11,000 --> 00:12:13,750
or Taiwan if the U.S. shows more support?

294
00:12:13,750 --> 00:12:15,450
You know, that's one of the things

295
00:12:15,450 --> 00:12:17,970
that that's funny about fear

296
00:12:17,970 --> 00:12:22,390
is sometimes people are the most afraid of
the unknown.

297
00:12:22,390 --> 00:12:24,220
And in many cases people didn't know.

298
00:12:24,220 --> 00:12:25,561
You know, if you're a diplomat

299
00:12:25,561 --> 00:12:28,339
at the state department and your boss asks
