00:12:37,820 --> 00:12:39,570
of something Taiwan is doing,

304
00:12:39,570 --> 00:12:42,860
or if I say something at the United Nations

305
00:12:42,860 --> 00:12:45,310
or something of that nature,

306
00:12:45,310 --> 00:12:49,820
in many cases a diplomat couldn't tell you.

307
00:12:49,820 --> 00:12:52,500
They wouldn't know, but there was a fear of,

