00:13:09,100 --> 00:13:11,290
And over time, that seemed to,

317
00:13:11,290 --> 00:13:13,149
at least in some cases,

318
00:13:13,149 --> 00:13:20,200
have a certain way of almost conditioning
people

319
00:13:20,200 --> 00:13:23,120
in the U.S. government to anticipate

