00:13:30,370 --> 00:13:33,329
what they didn't want and then to avoid that.

324
00:13:33,329 --> 00:13:35,140
It's hard to imagine that the U.S. government

325
00:13:35,140 --> 00:13:39,130
can be turned by an angry letter from Beijing.

326
00:13:39,130 --> 00:13:40,959
Not one, but if you imagine

327
00:13:40,959 --> 00:13:42,820
hundreds of thousands of them

328
00:13:42,820 --> 00:13:46,260
over a 40 year relationship

