00:14:06,750 --> 00:14:08,470
with the Chinese Communist Party.

337
00:14:08,470 --> 00:14:10,920
That also has obviously an effect as well.

338
00:14:10,920 --> 00:14:13,040
So what has the Chinese reaction been

339
00:14:13,040 --> 00:14:16,930
to this higher level of U.S. support for Taiwan?

340
00:14:16,930 --> 00:14:21,650
Chris, that is a really, really good question.

341
00:14:21,650 --> 00:14:25,300
In many ways, their reaction has not been
nearly

342
00:14:25,300 --> 00:14:27,810
as terrifying as I think

343
00:14:27,810 --> 00:14:32,700
what many people argued it would be.

344
00:14:32,700 --> 00:14:33,700
Certainly this was something

345
00:14:33,700 --> 00:14:35,850
people worried a lot about,

346
00:14:35,850 --> 00:14:37,920
what would their reaction be?

347
00:14:37,920 --> 00:14:40,959
And I think those that worried

348
00:14:40,959 --> 00:14:43,600
a lot of probably been a little disappointed

