00:14:48,980 --> 00:14:52,240
in support of Taiwan and not set off

352
00:14:52,240 --> 00:14:56,740
a potential crisis in the Taiwan Strait.

353
00:14:56,740 --> 00:14:58,610
How do you think the protests in Hong Kong

354
00:14:58,610 --> 00:15:01,470
have impacted Taiwan?

355
00:15:01,470 --> 00:15:04,800
Well, I think they've served as a wake up

356
00:15:04,800 --> 00:15:07,990
call for many people in Taiwan.

357
00:15:07,990 --> 00:15:10,170
For the past 20 years,

358
00:15:10,170 --> 00:15:12,010
those in Taiwan that favored

359
00:15:12,010 --> 00:15:15,600
a closer relationship with Beijing,

360
00:15:15,600 --> 00:15:19,900
argued that Hong Kong was a success story.

361
00:15:19,900 --> 00:15:22,610
That actually Hong Kong showed

362
00:15:22,610 --> 00:15:24,420
that you could be annexed

363
00:15:24,420 --> 00:15:25,529
by the Chinese Communist Party

364
00:15:25,529 --> 00:15:28,680
the way Hong Kong was back in '97

365
00:15:28,680 --> 00:15:30,620
and the results would not be so bad.

366
00:15:30,620 --> 00:15:35,720
And anybody who had visited Hong Kong before
this year,

367
00:15:35,720 --> 00:15:37,670
certainly before 2014,

368
00:15:37,670 --> 00:15:40,300
would say this is a very pleasant city-state.

369
00:15:40,300 --> 00:15:42,470
Very well run, very wealthy

370
00:15:42,470 --> 00:15:46,139
and a lot of great things going for it.

371
00:15:46,139 --> 00:15:49,370
And so there were those in Taiwan who said,

372
00:15:49,370 --> 00:15:50,860
Hey, maybe one country,

373
00:15:50,860 --> 00:15:53,240
two systems is not so bad.

374
00:15:53,240 --> 00:15:55,430
Maybe that could work for us too.

375
00:15:55,430 --> 00:15:57,110
Certainly that's what the Chinese Communist
Party

376
00:15:57,110 --> 00:15:58,240
wanted to promote,

377
00:15:58,240 --> 00:15:59,690
and it's something they did promote

378
00:15:59,690 --> 00:16:02,480
very heavily across the Taiwan Strait.

379
00:16:02,480 --> 00:16:03,760
Sort of like if the U.S.

380
00:16:03,760 --> 00:16:05,459
isn't giving us much support

381
00:16:05,459 --> 00:16:09,199
and the alternative is war invasion from China,

382
00:16:09,199 --> 00:16:11,529
why not do this seemingly better alternative

383
00:16:11,529 --> 00:16:13,760
of one country, two system?

384
00:16:13,760 --> 00:16:14,760
Exactly.

385
00:16:14,760 --> 00:16:19,860
The sense I think for some politicians in
Taiwan

386
00:16:19,860 --> 00:16:22,519
was that the United States had abandoned them
in 1979

387
00:16:22,519 --> 00:16:24,440
when we switched diplomatic relations.

