00:16:24,440 --> 00:16:26,410
And what would the PRC and not the ROC,

389
00:16:26,410 --> 00:16:29,160
the Republic of China,

390
00:16:29,160 --> 00:16:32,949
because previously before 1979 Taiwan

391
00:16:32,949 --> 00:16:34,779
was an ally of the United States.

392
00:16:34,779 --> 00:16:35,779
We had diplomatic relations,

393
00:16:35,779 --> 00:16:37,560
we had an embassy in Taipei,

394
00:16:37,560 --> 00:16:41,589
we had troops in Taiwan,

395
00:16:41,589 --> 00:16:44,560
we guarantee Taiwan's security.

396
00:16:44,560 --> 00:16:45,560
After that,

397
00:16:45,560 --> 00:16:46,910
there was a deep sense of betrayal,

398
00:16:46,910 --> 00:16:48,290
and there were those that said,

399
00:16:48,290 --> 00:16:49,529
well, the international community

400
00:16:49,529 --> 00:16:52,280
no longer recognizes us as a real country.

401
00:16:52,280 --> 00:16:56,330
The United States is keeping us at a distance.

402
00:16:56,330 --> 00:16:58,089
China's threatening us with war

