00:17:17,900 --> 00:17:20,559
I think it was a minority of people,

414
00:17:20,559 --> 00:17:23,779
perhaps a small minority,

415
00:17:23,779 --> 00:17:27,409
but that group has really diminished in size

416
00:17:27,409 --> 00:17:29,299
over the past six months,

417
00:17:29,299 --> 00:17:33,460
